      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 12 初六</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 12 初六</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初六，拔茅茹以其彙，貞吉。亨。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first SIX, divided, suggests the idea of grass pulled up, and bringing with it other stalks with whose roots it is connected. With firm correctness (on the part of its subject), there will be good fortune and progress.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
