      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 12 九五</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 12 九五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九五，休否，大人吉。其亡其亡，繫于苞桑。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In the fifth NINE, undivided, we see him who brings the distress and obstruction to a close,--the great man and fortunate. (But let him say), 'We may perish! We may perish!' (so shall the state of things become firm, as if) bound to a clump of bushy mulberry trees.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
