      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 12 上九</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 12 上九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>上九，傾否，先否後喜。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The sixth NINE, undivided, shows the overthrow (and removal of) the condition of distress and obstruction. Before this there was that condition. Hereafter there will be joy.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
